<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Appointment Notification</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;">

    <table role="presentation" style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #f8f8f8; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
                <img src="[Your Logo URL]" alt="Your Company Logo" style="max-width: 150px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px;">
                <h2 style="color: #333;">New Appointment Received</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">Hello Spa Des Epices Team,</p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">A new appointment request has been received. Here are the details:</p>
                <ul style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                    <li><strong>User's Name:</strong> {{fullName}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Time:</strong> {{time}}</li>
                </ul>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">Please take action by accepting or declining the appointment request.</p>
                <br>
                <table role="presentation">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="background-color: #4CAF50; padding: 10px 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px;">
                            <a href="https://spadesepices-admin.pages.dev?appointment_id={{id}}" style="color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px;">Check Appointment</a>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
                <br>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">Thank you for your attention. If you have any questions, please contact us.</p>
                <br>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">Best Regards,<br>Spa Des Epices</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>